        <mxCell id="Y1ChQ-webkH3Ca39AiPh-20" value="- Full Access to Corporate Systems&lt;div&gt;- Long-term account&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;- Subject to all Conditional Access Policies&lt;/div&gt;" style="whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;align=left;fillColor=#d5e8d4;strokeColor=#82b366;" parent="1" vertex="1">
