        <mxCell id="Y1ChQ-webkH3Ca39AiPh-21" value="&lt;div&gt;- Restricted to Project Specific Resources&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;- Limited Tenure (90-180 days)&lt;br&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;- No Access to Core Research Systems&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;- Same MFA requirements as employees&lt;/div&gt;" style="whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;align=left;fillColor=#dae8fc;strokeColor=#6c8ebf;" parent="1" vertex="1">
